Summary: On the NASA live video a satellite or UFO passed th Space Station
divs: Sighting DetailsI just saw a satellite or UFO pass the Space Station on the live NASA TV video during the STORMM trajectory test immediately surrounding the VH burn. It traveled vertically on the video with no transverse deviations. It looked like a satellite, but it was interesting. I had the U-verse DVR recording running at the time so it is stored in the U-verse box. You should review the NASA video at this time, if you have it, at around 11:50 PM PDT.
